OL,5, Hundreds of sex offenders across the UK
OL,6, slipped off the radar of police in a   
OL,7, three-year period, the BBC can reveal. 
OL,9,FFreedom of Information requests by BBC 
OL,10,FNews to 45 police forces reveal 729 sex
OL,11,Foffenders had gone missing or were     
OL,12,Fwanted for arrest from 2019-2021.      
OL,14,FAbuse survivors have called on the     
OL,15,Fgovernment to introduce a new law to   
OL,16,Fban sex offenders changing their names.
OL,18,FThe Home Office says it has "some of   
OL,19,Fthe toughest powers in the world to    
OL,20,Fdeal with sex offenders".              
